msgid "We make finding, buying and renting properties across Tanzania easier, safer and more transparent."
msgstr "Tunarahisisha kupata, kununua na kupanga mali kote Tanzania kwa njia rahisi, salama na wazi zaidi."

msgid "Owners upload ID when submitting ads, and admins review ads before they appear publicly."
msgstr "Wamiliki hupakia kitambulisho wanapowasilisha matangazo, na wasimamizi huhakiki matangazo kabla hayajaonekana hadharani."

